C. annulipes
]. Paratypes : 1♀ , “25, VII, 1936, Mt. Zaô, Takeuchi” [on upper side] “Col. K. Sirahata” [on underside]; 1♀ , “25, VII, 1939, Mt. Zao, Yamagata , Takeuchi” [on upper side] “[Ogura-sawa (in Japanese)], K. Sirahata” [on underside]; 2♀ 2♂ , “Mt. Zawosan, Miyagi Pref. , VII. 27. 1971 , A. Shinohara”.
